Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.57,0:01:48.70,Default1,46,0000,0000,0000,,露霜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.70,0:01:59.20,*Default5,47,0000,0000,0000,,所有的會員都是經過我們嚴格的審查才可以入會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.20,0:02:03.70,*Default5,48,0000,0000,0000,,所以絕對不會存在有可疑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.70,0:02:06.10,*Default5,49,0000,0000,0000,,或許該說是有問題的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.10,0:02:09.40,*Default5,50,0000,0000,0000,,如果會員間發生衝突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.40,*Default5,51,0000,0000,0000,,我們將會負責...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.40,0:02:14.20,*Default5,52,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}這就是我自己選擇的工作{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.00,0:02:20.20,*Default5,53,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}從三流大學的文學系畢業, 能找的工作有限{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.00,*Default5,54,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我是這麼想的{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.90,0:02:28.40,*Default5,55,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}不, 只是做我想做的{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.40,0:02:35.20,*Default5,56,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}其實我是想要體驗別人的快樂{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.10,0:02:38.00,*Default5,57,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}別人的悲傷{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.90,0:02:44.50,*Default5,58,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}特別想要待在人與人相遇與分離的地方{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.80,0:02:56.00,*Default5,59,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}那樣的話, 總有一天\N我想我也會變得跟他們一樣吧...{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.30,0:03:10.30,*Default5,60,0000,0000,0000,,以後也要更加努力地幫家裡忙唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.10,0:03:17.30,*Default5,61,0000,0000,0000,,耽誤到你不少時間, 總覺得有點對不起你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.70,*Default5,62,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛! 好像沒什麼精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.70,*Default5,63,0000,0000,0000,,你也要當哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.80,0:03:28.10,*Default5,64,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀! 快要生了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.60,*Default5,65,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.80,*Default5,66,0000,0000,0000,,小耕也是終於要當哥哥了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.90,0:03:51.30,*Default5,67,0000,0000,0000,,生了! 生了! 耕四郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.70,*Default5,68,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了, 是個女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.40,0:04:04.70,*Default5,69,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}總覺得有點高興又有點害怕{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.80,0:04:11.20,*Default5,70,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}但是, 那種心情只出現在那個時候{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.60,*Default5,71,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.80,*Default5,72,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.70,*Default5,73,0000,0000,0000,,妳想幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.20,*Default5,74,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 別...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.70,*Default5,75,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀啊呀! 你們在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.90,0:05:20.50,*Default5,76,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖, 怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.30,0:05:34.30,*Default5,77,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.40,0:05:38.70,*Default5,78,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖, 不哭, 不哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.40,*Default5,79,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我的錯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.40,*Default5,80,0000,0000,0000,,給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.40,*Default5,81,0000,0000,0000,,到底要不要呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.80,0:06:24.00,*Default5,82,0000,0000,0000,,我們不在的時候, 你沒欺負她吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.00,0:06:27.10,*Default5,83,0000,0000,0000,,七夏好像很怕你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.60,*Default5,84,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.50,*Default5,85,0000,0000,0000,,真拿妳沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.00,*Default5,86,0000,0000,0000,,不是我做的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.80,*Default5,87,0000,0000,0000,,不是指這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.90,0:07:01.30,*Default5,88,0000,0000,0000,,能來客廳一下嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.90,*Default5,89,0000,0000,0000,,並不是和妳母親彼此不和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.90,*Default5,90,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有大吵大鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.20,*Default5,91,0000,0000,0000,,只是呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.20,0:07:25.30,*Default5,92,0000,0000,0000,,在變成那樣子之前, 我們認為該分開生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.90,*Default5,93,0000,0000,0000,,嗯! 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.70,*Default5,94,0000,0000,0000,,讓你有痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.60,*Default5,95,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.90,*Default5,96,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是分開生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.50,*Default5,97,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是你的母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.50,0:07:40.10,*Default5,98,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子也仍然是你的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.10,*Default5,99,0000,0000,0000,,家人還是家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.10,*Default5,100,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.70,0:07:56.00,*Default5,101,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}在小時候來看, 離婚什麼的...\N並不是件平靜的事{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.30,0:08:03.60,*Default5,102,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我知道老爸或老媽為了我而平靜地離婚{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.40,*Default5,103,0000,0000,0000,,那麼, 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.90,0:08:19.30,*Default5,104,0000,0000,0000,,耕四郎, 交給你看家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.40,*Default5,105,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.50,0:08:25.00,*Default5,106,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.60,0:08:31.60,*Default5,107,0000,0000,0000,,別老是繃著臉唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.60,0:08:34.40,*Default5,108,0000,0000,0000,,要更加地坦率點, 知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.40,0:08:36.50,*Default5,109,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.20,*Default5,110,0000,0000,0000,,有空就來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.30,*Default5,111,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.30,*Default5,112,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了? 最近很早耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.10,*Default5,113,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.70,0:09:12.00,*Default5,114,0000,0000,0000,,大概迫不及待想見到七夏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.00,0:09:14.00,*Default5,115,0000,0000,0000,,我羨慕死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.40,0:09:18.70,*Default5,116,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 他又不是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:36.20,*Default5,117,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我...喜歡哥哥{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.90,0:09:55.00,*Default5,118,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}終究還是來了, 這是為什麼?{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.70,*Default5,119,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}自己也不是很清楚{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.30,0:10:12.10,*Default5,120,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我走在她還不認識我的時候所生活的城市{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.50,*Default5,121,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.20,*Default5,122,0000,0000,0000,,終於來到我家了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.40,*Default5,123,0000,0000,0000,,被妳認出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.80,*Default5,124,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的囉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.20,*Default5,125,0000,0000,0000,,你是耕四郎嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.30,*Default5,126,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為妳忘了我長什麼樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.30,*Default5,127,0000,0000,0000,,那你有忘了我的樣子了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.60,0:10:50.70,*Default5,128,0000,0000,0000,,你看, 雖然很多年沒見了\N但母子就是那樣呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.10,0:10:53.20,*Default5,129,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.50,*Default5,130,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.50,0:10:57.70,*Default5,131,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.80,0:10:59.90,*Default5,132,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.90,0:11:04.20,*Default5,133,0000,0000,0000,,你突然來了, 不是有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.10,*Default5,134,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.10,*Default5,135,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.70,*Default5,136,0000,0000,0000,,她小時候畫的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.20,*Default5,138,0000,0000,0000,,因為她最喜歡熊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.20,0:11:53.10,*Default5,139,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你的妹妹呢 在那一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.20,0:11:59.00,*Default5,140,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你們交換熊寶寶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.40,0:12:04.40,*Default5,141,0000,0000,0000,,暑假回來的時候, 七夏講得很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.70,*Default5,142,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓她住我家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.00,0:12:11.70,*Default5,143,0000,0000,0000,,離婚時妳把她帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.40,*Default5,144,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼現在突然給老爸照顧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.80,*Default5,145,0000,0000,0000,,因為...那邊的高中比較近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.10,*Default5,146,0000,0000,0000,,沒搞錯吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.40,0:12:25.70,*Default5,147,0000,0000,0000,,每天單程就要花兩小時以上太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.90,0:12:29.80,*Default5,148,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀? 想說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.80,0:12:30.90,*Default5,149,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.60,0:12:39.40,*Default5,150,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了? 只是來這裡鬧憋扭的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.50,*Default5,151,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.30,*Default5,152,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.80,*Default5,153,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.00,0:13:04.70,*Default5,154,0000,0000,0000,,沒剪你頭髮已經幾年了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.90,*Default5,155,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.90,0:13:10.60,*Default5,156,0000,0000,0000,,自從你當哥哥以後, 就不怎麼願意讓我剪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.60,*Default5,157,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你在固執什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.20,*Default5,158,0000,0000,0000,,"哥哥"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.50,*Default5,159,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.40,*Default5,160,0000,0000,0000,,她沒這樣煩你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.40,0:13:24.60,*Default5,161,0000,0000,0000,,"哥哥, 哥哥, 哥哥"的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.80,*Default5,162,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.10,*Default5,163,0000,0000,0000,,那是你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.60,0:13:34.50,*Default5,164,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}有哥哥是什麼樣的感覺呢?{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.20,*Default5,165,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}真想快點見到他{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.40,*Default5,166,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}也許他會教我功課{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.40,*Default5,167,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}啊! 沒什麼沒什麼{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.80,*Default5,168,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}他一定會教妳功課的{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.90,*Default5,169,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}嗯!{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.20,0:14:01.80,*Default5,170,0000,0000,0000,,非常想和你們...\N不如說是, 想和你一起生活呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.60,*Default5,171,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.40,*Default5,172,0000,0000,0000,,所以那孩子就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.40,0:14:10.90,*Default5,173,0000,0000,0000,,善三在關鍵時刻是靠不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.10,*Default5,174,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.10,0:14:16.90,*Default5,175,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼? 打起精神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.60,*Default5,176,0000,0000,0000,,你是哥哥吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.90,0:14:32.70,*Default5,178,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓她不幸該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.70,0:14:33.90,*Default5,179,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.00,0:14:40.80,*Default5,180,0000,0000,0000,,如果我做了讓她不幸的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.30,*Default5,181,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.20,*Default5,182,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.60,*Default5,183,0000,0000,0000,,那我可是不會放過你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.40,*Default5,184,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.00,*Default5,185,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.00,0:15:11.00,*Default5,186,0000,0000,0000,,還是跟以前一樣不坦率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.00,0:15:12.10,*Default5,187,0000,0000,0000,,應該吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.10,0:15:15.90,*Default5,188,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說你一點都沒長大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.00,*Default5,189,0000,0000,0000,,振作點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.80,*Default5,190,0000,0000,0000,,她現在會有許多的困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.80,0:15:23.60,*Default5,191,0000,0000,0000,,在那種年齡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.40,0:15:30.90,*Default5,192,0000,0000,0000,,難得來一次, 也不多待一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.20,*Default5,193,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.80,*Default5,194,0000,0000,0000,,我明天還要上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.80,*Default5,195,0000,0000,0000,,記得一定要吃飯唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.80,0:15:36.60,*Default5,196,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:40.50,*Default5,197,0000,0000,0000,,對了, 七夏煮的菜口味有點重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.60,*Default5,198,0000,0000,0000,,叫她注意點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.60,0:15:42.60,*Default5,199,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.60,0:15:46.00,*Default5,200,0000,0000,0000,,還有不要給她太多的零用錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.40,*Default5,201,0000,0000,0000,,就算她跟我要, 我也不會給她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.10,*Default5,202,0000,0000,0000,,還有叫她別太晚睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.70,*Default5,203,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦! 要趕不上電車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.70,0:15:53.60,*Default5,204,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.50,*Default5,205,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.20,*Default5,206,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.90,*Default5,207,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你了, 耕四郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.80,0:16:08.10,*Default5,208,0000,0000,0000,,喔! 走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.90,*Default5,209,0000,0000,0000,,兄妹要好好相處唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.90,*Default5,210,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.90,*Default5,211,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.20,*Default5,212,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦! 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.60,0:19:11.10,*Default5,213,0000,0000,0000,,我...我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.30,*Default5,214,0000,0000,0000,,要嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.60,0:20:02.70,*Default5,215,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.60,*Default5,216,0000,0000,0000,,不哭了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.60,*Default5,217,0000,0000,0000,,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.50,*Default5,218,0000,0000,0000,,不, 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.10,0:20:19.70,*Default5,219,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.30,0:20:23.00,*Default5,220,0000,0000,0000,,今天去哪裡了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.70,*Default5,221,0000,0000,0000,,某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.40,*Default5,222,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.50,*Default5,223,0000,0000,0000,,散步啦散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.50,0:20:30.00,*Default5,224,0000,0000,0000,,所以說去哪裡了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.50,*Default5,225,0000,0000,0000,,某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.00,0:20:36.90,*Default5,226,0000,0000,0000,,真是的, 帶我一起去就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.10,*Default5,227,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}哥哥也好{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.00,0:20:50.00,*Default5,228,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}和平相處的兄妹也好{\i0}
