Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.60,*Default5,230,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}無論怎樣我都會做我該做的{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.00,*Default5,231,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}所以...{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.30,0:21:03.30,*Default5,232,0000,0000,0000,,妳明天要早起吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.00,*Default5,233,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.50,*Default5,234,0000,0000,0000,,但是哥哥你也要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.50,0:21:09.10,*Default5,235,0000,0000,0000,,我抽根煙再去睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.20,*Default5,236,0000,0000,0000,,去睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.00,*Default5,237,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.40,*Default5,238,0000,0000,0000,,我洗吧
